  "body": "- [âœ… ] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\nOn running ```truffle test``` or ```truffle migrate```\r\n\r\n```Something went wrong while attempting to connect to the network```\r\n```Could not connect to your Ethereum client```\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/39130640/128458816-59853277-acb8-4b63-b5fa-7ef2f2c58ff8.png)\r\n\r\n**here is my truffle config**\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/39130640/128458952-3f455134-1d42-43fa-816c-355bb20646b3.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\nMinimal Reproduction: \r\n```truffle unbox metacoin```\r\n_uncomment development and test networks_\r\n\r\nnow try running ```truffle test``` or ```truffle migrate```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Ubuntu 20.04 \r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.4.3\r\n* node version (`node --version`): 14.17.1\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 7.18.1\r\n",
